isMultipartContent

public static boolean isMultipartContent(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request)
Tells if a request is multipart or not.

Parameters:
request - the javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest that we are going to check.
Returns:
true if the request is multipart, false otherwise.

parse

public void parse(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request,
                  PartHandler partHandler)
           throws IOException,
                  MultipartException
Parses a multipart request calling the PartHandler callbacks when a part is found.

Parameters:
request - the javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest that we are going to parse.
partHandler - a callback handler that will be called when a part is found.
Throws:
IOException - if there is a problem parsing the request.
MultipartException - if the request is not multipart or if there is an error parsing the multipart request.
